
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .header { padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; background-color: #f8f8f8; }
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; line-height: 1.6; text-align: left; }
        .button-container { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer { padding: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #777; background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="DevGo Logo" style="width: 150px; height: auto;" />
            <h2 style="margin-top: 10px;">Welcome to DevGo!</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{fullName}},</p>

            <p>We're thrilled to have you with us. Your account has been successfully created using your Google account.</p>
            
            <p>You can now start booking parcels, tracking your deliveries, and much more. Click the button below to go to your dashboard.</p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" target="_blank" class="button">Go to My Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Thanks for choosing DevGo!<br>
            <strong>The DevGo Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 DevGo. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>